description:
With the Spotify app, you can explore an extensive library of music and podcasts for free. Curate the best playlists and stream millions of free songs, albums and original podcasts on your mobile or tablet. Subscribe to Spotify Premium to download and listen offline wherever you are, and unlock our catalogue of audiobooks.

Why choose Spotify as your go-to music and podcast app? Here, you can:
• Listen to over 100 million songs and 6 million podcast titles
• Explore our selection of specially-crafted artist playlists
• Easily search for your favourite songs, albums, artists and podcasts
• Discover personalised music recommendations tailored to your unique taste
• Subscribe to your favourite free podcasts so you never miss an episode and even curate your own podcast library

Spotify Free is more than a music player – find the sounds that you love and stream music and podcasts online for free. Enjoy personalised playlists or curate and share your own, discover the hottest new releases, explore upcoming events from your favourites and more.

• Stream millions of free songs and podcasts
• Create playlists with your favourite music
• Share songs and playlists with friends and family (feature restrictions may apply in some regions)
• Discover personalised playlists made just for you, and collaborate on playlists with your friends
• Enjoy your personal Discover Weekly playlist every week
• Stay in the know with the Release Radar and New Music Friday playlists
• Find nearby events and gigs by your favourite artists
• See your most played songs, genres, artists and more with yearly Spotify Wrapped
• Stream music across your devices with Spotify
• Use Spotify Connect and enjoy listening on smart speakers, desktop, laptop, smart TV, Chromecast, PlayStation®, Xbox®, smartwatch, in your car and more – limited number of device models apply

Spotify Premium – a great way to enjoy the benefits of an offline music player and stream music without Wi-Fi. By pressing download, you can access your songs, playlists, podcasts and audiobooks offline, wherever you are.
• Listen to music, podcasts and audiobooks – all in one place
• Ad-free music listening: enjoy your music with no ad interruptions
• Enjoy full on-demand playback
• Audiobooks in Premium are currently available in the UK, US, Australia, Ireland, New Zealand and Canada. Discover 250,000+ audiobook titles with 15 hours/month of available listening for Premium Individual subscribers and Duo & Family plan managers.
• Superior sound quality on supported devices
• AI DJ: a personalised guide that knows your music taste so well that it can choose what to play for you
• Enjoy on desktop, mobile phone, tablet, computer, smartwatch and in your car
• Listen and control the listening session together by hosting a Jam in real time with friends
• Download songs, podcasts and audiobooks for offline listening without an Internet connection
• No contract required – cancel your subscription whenever you want

Spotify lets you play music wherever you are. Listen to your favourite songs and discover new music, podcasts and audiobooks with the Spotify app!

Tired of being restricted by Wi-Fi or network when listening to your favorite music?
Imagine a world where you can immerse yourself in music anytime, anywhere, without relying on an internet connection.

Now! We proudly present ASMR Musi, the ultimate solution for your music playback needs.

Asmr Musi is an all-in-one audio app designed to provide users with a complete audio journey. The app brings together a variety of soundscapes such as the crunch of chewing, the rustle of turning pages, the sound of soft whispers, the warmth of wood, the crinkling of packaging, the melodies of instruments, the click of nails, the scribbles of pens, and more.

Each auditory selection has been carefully curated to provide the best relaxation experience.
The app has an intuitive and easy-to-use interface that easily guides users through various sound categories and allows users to save bookmarks based on their personal preferences. For those who want to keep their unique auditory moments forever, the in-app recording feature is a perfect solution. It allows users to capture, edit recordings, and manage their audio library by removing outdated tracks, ensuring a fresh and tailored listening experience at all times.

What's that song? Shazam will instantly identify music playing around you or in apps like TikTok, Instagram, YouTube & Snapchat. Discover concerts near you, song lyrics, videos & more. With tens of millions of daily users, Shazam is trusted by music lovers worldwide.

“Shazam is a gift... a game changer” – Pharrell Williams, GQ 
“I don't know how we ever survived before Shazam” – Marshmello 
“Shazam is a kind of magic… You hear a song, hold your phone up like a wand and it tells you exactly what song it is, who sang it and lets you add it to your playlist or share it to your social media… How is that not magic?!” – Calum Scott

WHY YOU’LL LOVE IT

* Identify music in an instant.
* Discover live shows near you from your favourite artists or through curated recommendations.
* Recognise songs even when you’re offline, using headphones or on a different app.
* Revisit your music discovery history in your library anytime.
* Get recommended songs and playlists similar to the music you’ve discovered.

USE SHAZAM ANYWHERE, ANYTIME

* Enable the Shazam widgets on your Lock Screen or Home Screen.
* Ask Siri, “What’s this song?” to use Shazam hands-free.
* Automate music discovery with the Shazam Shortcut in the Shortcuts app.

CONNECT WITH YOUR MUSIC

* Unlock extras from artists around the world.
* Open any song directly in Apple Music, Spotify, YouTube Music, Amazon Music & Deezer.
* Listen and add songs directly to your Apple Music playlists.
* Watch music videos of the songs you discover in Apple Music or YouTube.
* Follow along to songs with real-time, karaoke-style lyrics.
* See what’s trending locally and globally with Shazam Charts.

Availability and features may vary by country. For more information on Shazam’s privacy practices, please read the Privacy Policy, available at https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/. Find out more and get support from AppleCare at https://support.apple.com/guide/shazam/welcome.

Become a DJ with the YouDJ Mixer, it is super easy! 

Hey I am Erik, the solo programmer of YouDJ. I worked by passion for 15 years to build this app, that's why this app is absolutely free with no ads, for reel, you can see by yourself! 

With the YouDJ mixer, you can mix like a pro with no preliminary knowledge. This app is all about giving you an easy and intuitive interface that even your grandma can use!

YouDJ offers a range of cool features and DJ tools for you to have fun. While it mays not be the most complete DJ app, we offer you the must-have, high quality, DJ tools that will take your mixes to the next level.

From 16 sound effects and an 80 sounds sampler to vinyl scratching, auto beat synchronization, keylock, loops, automix, and hot cues. These features will ensure you have everything you need to unleash your creativity.

The YouDJ mixer comes preloaded with a collection of music, but you can also play MP3 files stored on your device.

It's important to understand that no DJ app, including YouDJ, can integrate with Apple Music, Spotify, or YouTube Music due to their closed platforms and the DRM encryption on their songs. Also, legally mixing popular music without paying on mobile platforms doesn't exist unfortunately.

The YouDJ Mixer is available on all desktop and mobile platforms, so you can rock the party wherever you go. But we highly recommend you to try the computer version too (you.dj).

So, what are you waiting for? 

Grab your headphones, download YouDJ, and start your DJ journey today!

If you appreciate the effort I've invested in developing this app without any coin, make sure to leave a review. It seriously means the world to me and helps me out big time.

Much love and thanks in advance!

Erik the programmer

—------------------------------

How to Mix:

You're equipped with a classic DJ setup featuring two turntables and a mixer. 
Your mission? Simultaneously unleash the magic of two songs, each playing on its respective turntable, and then skillfully blend them together using the mixer. 

To spice up your mix, you can use effects such as the loops, the fx pads, the eq, the scratch, the sampler, the hot cues.
—------------------------------

Shoutout to all of you for showing mad love to YouDJ. It seriously keeps me hyped to keep this project going!

Go ahead and have fun with YouDJ!

Erik the programmer

app_name: DJ Mixer Studio - DJ Music Mix
description:
Coocent DJ is perfect for both beginner and professional DJs, with an intuitive interface that makes it easy to mix and blend tracks together seamlessly. With a variety of features, including customizable sound effects, loops, and beat matching, you can create a unique and unforgettable mix that will keep your audience dancing all night long. 

Coocent DJ - DJ Mixer Studio is an real DJ mixer and music mixer with sound effects, Equalizer & Bass Booster to remix songs, make music and record mixes on the go. With Coocent DJ - DJ Music Mixer, you can create and customize your music mixes with ease, using a range of powerful mixing tools, effects, and loops. 

Coocent DJ - DJ Mix Studio is a powerful and intuitive music mixing app that allows users to unleash their creativity and become a DJ right from their smartphones or tablets. With a wide range of features and effects, this app provides an immersive DJ experience for beginners and professionals alike. 
If you are looking for an virtual DJ mixer or music mixer app, if you want to create your won music beat, This excellent music DJ mixer makes it easy for creative people and music lovers like you!

Easy-to-Use Interface
DJ Music mixer offers a user-friendly interface with intuitive controls, making it easy for anyone to start mixing tracks and creating their own unique sound.

Virtual Turntables
Get the feel of traditional DJing with virtual turntables that allow you to scratch, mix, and blend tracks seamlessly. Bring out your inner DJ and create smooth transitions between songs.

Music Library
Access your personal music library or explore a vast selection of tracks from various online platforms. Import your favorite songs and create playlists for your DJ sets.

Crossfader and EQ Controls
Adjust the audio levels and equalizer settings to perfect your mix. Use the crossfader to smoothly transition between songs and maintain a seamless flow of music.

Effects and Filters
Enhance your mix with a variety of effects, including reverb, delay, flanger, and more. Apply filters to manipulate the sound and add a personal touch to your DJ sets.

Looping and Remixing
Experiment with loops and samples to create unique remixes on the fly. Loop sections of a song to extend the beats, or mix in samples to add extra layers to your mix.

Real-Time Recording
Capture your DJ sets in real-time and save them as high-quality audio files. Share your mixes with friends or showcase your talent to the world.

Live Performance Features
Connect your device to external speakers or headphones for a professional DJ setup. Perform live at parties, events, or even in the comfort of your own home.

Whether you're a beginner looking to explore the world of DJing or a seasoned professional wanting a portable mixing solution, DJ Music mixer - DJ Mix Studio has everything you need to create impressive mixes and entertain your audience. Download now and unleash your DJ skills wherever you go!
